</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C337088DF77CB13DB182F860302F449F" pageId="9" pageNumber="530" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F77CB13DB182F860302F449F" blockId="9.[151,1437,1447,2013]" pageId="9" pageNumber="530">COMMENTS: The original label on NRM 569751 is missing. Dates and places agree with the journal entries and Sundevall’s acquisition catalogue.</paragraph>
